This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) category as it deals with image segmentation. The use of an adversarial network also suggests that it could belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) or artificial intelligence (cs.AI) categories. The fact that the paper focuses on medical imaging and specifically chest X-rays suggests that it could also belong to the medical imaging (cs.MED) or information retrieval (cs.IR) categories.
